  ('dietitian-moex-05486', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關單碳代謝（one-carbonmetabolism）調節之敘述，下列何者正確？', '["維生素B 缺乏會導致5-甲基四氫葉酸（5-methyltetrahydrofolate）累積 12", "維生素B缺乏會導致5,10-亞甲基四氫葉酸（5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate）累積 2", "四氫葉酸（tetrahydrofolate）轉變成5,10-亞甲基四氫葉酸（5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate）需要 羥丁胺酸（threonine）提供甲基", "5,10-亞甲基四氫葉酸（5,10-methylenetetrahydrofolate）轉變成5-甲基四氫葉酸（5-methyltetrahydrofolate） 可將甲基轉移至甘胺酸（glycine）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dd78b1c2d1f2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "beeb66af7964", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 38, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-05487', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-109-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '與呼吸鏈的複合體II緊密結合的檸檬酸循環的酵素是：', '["琥珀酸去氫酶（succinatedehydrogenase）", "蘋果酸去氫酶（malatedehydrogenase）", "異檸檬酸去氫酶（isocitratedehydrogenase）", "α-酮戊二酸去氫酶（α-ketoglutarate dehydrogenase）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:41+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "dd78b1c2d1f2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "beeb66af7964", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "109110", "c": "103", "s": "0201", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "109", "exam_name": "109年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、109年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
